{"title":"春光曲（诗三首）","authors":["李村"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":4,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春光曲（诗三首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李村"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汽笛催春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰融雪化风软，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迷漫晨雾炊烟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝霞城边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里田园。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火车声声远去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汽笛催春过苍江。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼里盼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里牵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社千秋又一年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义花映路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一程一程朝阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春光好"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田园无边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天脚云远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拖拉机在田间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马达声醉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流水声喧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹花头巾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁家女驾驶员？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布谷声声近又远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火车噗噗村边过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声汽笛响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里河山绿遍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蝶飞花舞忆江南"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春水渡头人不断，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蝶飞花舞忆江南。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水田明似镜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"菜花黄接天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满山杜鹃摇红影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田头江畔人正勤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记得跃进头一年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社初建，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村村锣鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遍地歌声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舞影翩翩阳江城。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此年年花争艳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春光总无限。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}